
Installation Instructions
*************************

To compile it you need Audacious 3.6 and libmaclib 4.11

Libmaclib you can download from https://sourceforge.net/projects/maclib/
For easy installation process on ubuntu or debian please, copy macadd/* to root directory of maclib source and run mk.sh


--------------------
Compile:
--------------------
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure --prefix=/usr
$ make -j

-------------------
Install
------------------

sudo make install

That's all
